<plot>Gubston Rundelcake (Scott Tosta), a bumbling appliance salesman, thought his day would be like any other. Along a deserted highway Gubston's day goes horribly wrong when his car careens into a mysterious Pedestrian (Brian Sharp). Suddenly his world is turned upside down when his haphazard attempt to cover up his crime becomes a fight to stay alive in the bizarre town of Blaton.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581882</url></doc>
